Why don't start by looking at packages snow and snowfall?
They support what you want to do without the hassles to setup a private 
cloud (for this check project eucalyptus).
Take a look also to the CRAN HPC task page for ideas.
For openCL start looking at Rgpu.
Hope it helps
			mario

